Package cpg.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckBoxCellFactory
    Helper class to make a CheckBox inside a TableCell.
    FileHandler
    This is a helper class to load data from a file into a WordList or save data from a WordList to a file.
    KeywordComparator
    A helper class to compare two keywords of a Word, specially for sorting the Words in a WordList alphabetically.
    MapSortByValue
    Helper class to sort a map by its value (instead of by its keyword).
    SVGMakery
    This is a helper class in order to save a crossword that is represented as a 2-dimensional string array as a SVG file.
    WordStatistics
    This is a helper class that provides information about the German language letter frequencies.
